```plantuml
@startuml adityajain10_foot365-live-streaming-chatbot-prediction-app-on-aws

actor User
participant "Frontend (Browser)" as Frontend
participant "API Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "Lambda Function: LF1" as LF1
participant "Lambda Function: LF2" as LF2
participant "Lex" as Lex
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "ElasticSearch" as ElasticSearch
participant "SageMaker" as SageMaker
participant "SNS" as SNS
participant "SQS" as SQS

User -> Frontend: Access web application
Frontend -> APIGateway: GET /fixtures
APIGateway -> LF1: Invoke LF1
LF1 -> ElasticSearch: Query fixtures
ElasticSearch -> LF1: Return fixtures
LF1 -> APIGateway: Response with fixtures
APIGateway -> Frontend: Return fixtures
Frontend -> APIGateway: POST /predict
APIGateway -> LF1: Invoke LF1
LF1 -> SageMaker: Request prediction
SageMaker -> LF1: Return prediction
LF1 -> APIGateway: Response with prediction
APIGateway -> Frontend: Return prediction
Frontend -> APIGateway: POST /chatbot
APIGateway -> LF2: Invoke LF2
LF2 -> Lex: Process user input
Lex -> LF2: Return intent
alt Intent: Get Fixtures
    LF2 -> ElasticSearch: Query fixtures
    ElasticSearch -> LF2: Return fixtures
else Intent: Send SMS
    LF2 -> SNS: Send SMS
    SNS -> LF2: SMS Sent
end
LF2 -> SQS: Queue response
LF2 -> DynamoDB: Store chat history
LF2 -> APIGateway: Response to chatbot
APIGateway -> Frontend: Return chatbot response

@enduml
```